QuestData.Title: The Waters of Teldrassil
QuestData.Description: Our tasks are done here for now. This water proved to be of great importance, but it wasn't originally meant for me. Go ahead and bring it back to Corithras at the crossroads, I'm sure he'd like you to deliver it to its original destination.
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring the Filled Vessel to Corithras Moonrage at the crossroads in front of Darnassus.
QuestData.CompletionText: It is good to see you again. I sense that Tarindrella's task went smoothly with you by her side.
QuestData.RewardText: Thank you for returning to me so swiftly. I have but one last task to ask of you. Shall we?
